  "title": "Internal Auditor – Fintech (Taiwan based)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Rare opportunity</li><li>Startup environment</li><li>Opportunity for career growth</li></ul><p>A Fintech client is seeking an  <strong>Internal Auditor </strong> to join the team.This is a pioneer headcount in the Internal Audit team, responsible for end-to-end execution of audit including planning, execution in accordance with Taiwan’s regulatory requirements. Your role will also look at internal controls, AML/CFT reviews and end to end business operations processes. This is an excellent opportunity for those who want to have ownership of their own work, and work in a fast-paced dynamic environment.</p><p>The ideal candidate should have at least 4 years relevant experience within audit for a Financial services firm preferably within fintech – blockchain, crypto, digital wallet etc. Taiwan FSC regulatory knowledge is a must, and other AML/CFT regulations for the fintech environment will be highly advantageous. Strong communication skills in both English and Mandarin is required for internal & external communications and engagement</p><p>If you are keen, please click on the link to apply or email me with your updated CV at Rachel.ljy@ethosbc.com. Look forward to hearing back, thank you.<br /></p><p>Reg. No. R1987809<br />BeathChapman Pte Ltd<br />Licence no. 16S8112</p>",
